text: Angelika Beblo (born 11 March 1961) is a German rower. She competed in two events at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:German female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of West Germany Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saarbrücken
